
How to use dpns common functions in other modules?

use follow function to get dpns common pdev and you will get dpns common priv
==== code start =====
struct platform_device * common_pdev = NULL;
struct device * common_dev = NULL;
COMMON_t * common_priv = NULL;
common_dev = bus_find_device_by_name(&platform_bus_type, NULL, "11000000.dpnsCommon");
if (common_dev) {
	common_pdev = to_platform_device(common_dev);
	if (common_pdev)
		common_priv = platform_get_drvdata(common_pdev);
}
==== code end =====
